<space/>II. <rs type="pers" ana="n_84747" ref="#fk__p_46919"><seg type="spc">Nestroy</seg></rs>: <rs type="title">Das Lied von der Chimäre</rs>. — <rs type="pers" ana="n_84748" ref="#fk__p_43433">Frank Wedekind<lb/>
