            <p ana="pr138168">
<space/>II. Einleitung. — <rs type="pers" ana="n_84755" ref="#fk__p_46919"><seg type="spc">Nestroy</seg></rs>: <rs type="title"><seg type="spc">Weder Lorbeerbaum noch<lb/>
